snippet.title: BYTE - 90 Second Trailer
snippet.description:
Did you know that BYTE has new visuals with a brand-new rendering system? Now you do, and you can play it right now!

This is a 90-second look at BYTE, a tactics RPG and visual novel based on "Dracula" by Bram Stoker!

Learn more about BYTE: https://jamesmartini.me/byte/
Play BYTE now! https://jamesmartini.itch.io/byte
